front.title: •Sacrifice
front.gametext: Reduce your battle damage by 5 by losing from hand a starship, vehicle or character. OR If your character's forfeit was just reduced to 0, restore it to normal. (Immune to Sense.)
front.lore: Jabba's minions could be expected to be sacrificed to save the Hutt, to destroy one of the Hutts enemies or to provide the Hutt and his minions with a good laugh.
